&lt;table class="data __useTableEditor"&gt;&lt;thead&gt;
  &lt;tr&gt;
   
   &lt;th&gt;Description&lt;/th&gt;
   
   &lt;th&gt;File&lt;/th&gt;
   
   &lt;th&gt;Date&lt;/th&gt;
   
  &lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/thead&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;
  &lt;tr&gt;
   
   &lt;td&gt;Bad pixel map. Value 1 = bad pixel.&lt;br class="" /&gt;&lt;br class="" /&gt;Full frame (1024x512)&lt;br class="" /&gt;Strip mode (1024x300)&lt;br class="" /&gt;Stamp mode (400x200)&lt;br class="" /&gt;Substamp mode (100x50)&lt;br class="" /&gt;&lt;br class="" /&gt;(Or see &lt;a href="/groups/clio2usermanual/wiki/3a7bb/Full_Frame_and_Sub_Frame_Formats.html"&gt;Full Frame and Sub Frame Formats&lt;/a&gt; for how to crop the full-frame images yourself.)&lt;/td&gt;
   
