   &lt;td&gt;Calibrated 2013/04/10 from data from April 2013 -- NOT VALID FOR 2014B DATA. Check your FITS header. The linearity data have Temp1=54.999K and VOS=2.5 Volts (Bias voltage). Only valid for these parameters.&lt;/td&gt;
   
