   &lt;td&gt;Plate scale and instrument angle (&amp;quot;North_Clio&amp;quot;), and IDL program to rotate North up (.pro).&lt;/td&gt;
   
   &lt;td&gt;Get Platescale and NorthClio instrument angle at &lt;a href="/groups/clio2usermanual/wiki/d017e/Astrometric_Calibration.html"&gt;Astrometric Calibration&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br class="" /&gt;DEROT = ROTOFF-180+NORTHCLIO&lt;br class="" /&gt;&lt;img src="/groups/clio2usermanual/wiki/6d927/attachments/63923/derot_clio.pro.png" alt="Download file &amp;quot;derot_clio.pro&amp;quot;" title="Download file &amp;quot;derot_clio.pro&amp;quot;" class="attachment_handle_img" longdesc="/groups/clio2usermanual/wiki/6d927/attachments/63923/derot_clio.pro" /&gt;&lt;br class="" /&gt;To rotate your images to get North up:&lt;br class="" /&gt;Rotate COUNTER-CLOCKWISE by angle DEROT.&lt;/td&gt;
   
